"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"77c82afdb9325430a28db064c04a617b950f83a0","tid":2409603,"uid":358892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"做coding唔係老咗唔夠班後生砌？<br />\n唔諗住升management或者可能自己開公司？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"老咗或者打code無咁快但經驗搭夠。BTW，software engineer工作需要coding但coding唔係工作全部，有其他野做，例如design，trouble shooting，performance analysis，lead project等，好多野有經驗會有效率過齋打code打得快。<br />\n<br />\n我無諗住行management track，都係鍾意行technical。有啲公司有dual career track，可以揀行management定technical，兩邊有對等嘅職級。我有試過同我manager同grade。做生意不是我杯茶，我打工會開心啲。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"外國大把4，50歲engineers<br />\n但香港班毒撚零溝通技巧就轉便PM<br />\n最後做到一鑊泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"諗起James Gosling都幾乎冇人請單嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537603bce709d8508858c4c28497979e73199db3","tid":2409603,"uid":335583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbcd1ae5a92873f43d58767da482ecc9ab218501","tid":2409603,"uid":358892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1257fa43475b73d88065c909bf285ee8069c5b88","tid":2409603,"uid":335583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d6f501d65d41287354ebd80da4874d3194d8704","tid":2409603,"uid":358892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"尚愛programming嗎？<br />\n未來點打算？<br />\n新仔成日畀人叫去寫test code<br />\n好撚悶<br />\n想開發多啲<br />\n上司又好日都唔揾我<br />\nWfh瞓到狗咁都冇人知<br />\n好不安"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"Wtf?<br />\n日日返工做乜？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/n